1. Ona je *gotovo* rekla sve što je imala da kaže. (She almost said everything she had to say.)
2. *Gotovo* je bilo priče, pa je otišla. (Almost all the talking was done, so she left.)
3. Oni su *gotovo* udvostručili svoj profit. (They almost doubled their profit.)
4. *Gotovo* sam siguran da će oni uspeti. (I'm almost certain they will succeed.) 
5. *Gotovo* smo stigli. (We almost arrived.)